➜宽哥：《水龙吟.客河源客家小镇》
http://www.sohu.com/a/429038571_100115135	55273
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201102/79bb011d4eea4c97b03ab7d27d7c8e9e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《水龙吟.客河源客家小镇》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>———词林正韵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 文/宽哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青砖碧瓦飞甍，朱帘绣阁连亭榭。琴韵悠悠，彩衣轻舞，笛声盈夜。叹人流如织，酒旗斜矗，俏面红，月高挂。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好梦犹如风絮。忆佳期、温馨如画。汤泉吐艳，暗香幽径，浮生闲暇。百味丰肴，客家清醴，盛情难谢。盼来年归雁，松风把盏，龙吟续写。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201102/17fc69315ad5457493f6d8e4d4affd22.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
