➜广西诗人陈熠明：梦幻弦音碧月生
http://www.sohu.com/a/429040786_100115135	55969
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201102/fdce3e7121e442d49c4c73ab5366f69a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>梦幻弦音碧月生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(一)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·梵音曲落向天涯</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长风彼岸云霞幻，剑海潮生笑雨花。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">浪涌江湖飞远梦，梵音曲落向天涯。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(二)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·日影飞花云海上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">情缘岛上梦烟无，曲奏涛声浪远出。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日影飞花云海上，天涯彼岸笑江湖。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(三)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·云边曲落风随意</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">浪里相逢烟雨岸，缠绵不舍问天长。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云边曲落风随意，碧海兰舟梦远方。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201102/81d199aa73e04de6a2f44e44879c2eb2.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(四)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·情弦水上流真韵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万里云霞映曙光，江湖梦海浪飞扬。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">情弦水上流真韵，曲落涛声动远方。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(五)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·云风曲上有丹心</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流波荡漾倚天琴，彼岸方舟唱水音。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">碧海飞花烟雨幻，云风曲上有丹心。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(六)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·爱恨情仇烟海落</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">山重水复引花明，涛飞琴弦碧月清。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱恨情仇烟海落，江湖水浪雨风平。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201102/c55b3631d3904f65aa64a4352970968d.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(七)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·，云边泪落琴弦梦</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">破浪长风心有愿，春华望断雨烟摇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云边泪落琴弦梦，碧海涛声荡远箫。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(八)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·梦幻弦音碧月生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">落影狂花应水风，烟波万里泪相逢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云飞瀚海潮流远，梦幻弦音碧月生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(九)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·追寻彼岸流波影</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">追寻彼岸流波影，瀚海兰舟梦远高。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唱罢流云君子浪，弦音水笑荡今朝。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201102/8e1387a7d9f44a719665e4002e2b8d94.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·涛飞彼岸醉弦音</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">江湖往事影留心，玉海风潮落烟琴，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">碧月云边追远梦，涛飞彼岸醉弦音。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十一)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·剑影潮飞问倚天</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">望远江湖风雨静，长风海岸梦情缘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">桃花岛上留弦月，剑影潮飞问倚天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十二)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·随缘浪里笑相逢</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等你潮前旭日升，随缘浪里笑相逢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云霞作伴清风远，梦海弦音富水生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201102/c32a9d8d29bf487d8961733d6149991c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>陈熠明，笔名心灵诗幻，男，1976年生，广西平果市人。爱好文学创作，曾有诗歌作品发布于多家报刊杂志和网络。时任星连文学社副社长。职业于中医，热衷于传统文化传播。诗是文笔与文笔的向往，诗是朋友与朋友的交心。诗是千难和万险的将来，诗是岁月与年华的渴望。诗是春夏和秋冬的风景，诗是父亲和母亲的嘱咐，诗是父亲和母亲的叮咛。诗是渡船与碧波的远航，诗是生命与大海的彼岸。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201102/8df07695eb294c82b930730d7ff94315.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>❖星连文学社管理团队：</strong></p>
<p>★ <strong>名誉社长:</strong>叶仲录 ☆<strong>总顾问:</strong>薛依云 ☆<strong>首席顾问:</strong>欧大象 ☆<strong>执行顾问:</strong>岩心（薛莹） ☆<strong>顾问团成员:</strong>欧大象（文光）、岩心（薛莹）、石秉旺、陈文化、高原红、碧海（陈碧珍)、黄香玉 ☆<strong>社长兼总编:</strong>星连 ☆<strong>常务副社长:</strong>岩心（薛莹） ☆<strong>副社长:</strong>丁冬亮、绝尘道长、梁继权、高晓园、陈熠明、东晓 、木子 ☆<strong>艺术总监:</strong>陆廷教 ☆<strong>编委会主任:</strong>听尘居士 ☆<strong>编委会成员:</strong>孤客、黄香玉、星连、枫叶、绮雯、徐玉兰、叶仲录、薛依云、高晓园、田书芹、木子……（添加中） ☆<strong>主编:</strong>游散居士 ☆<strong>副主编：</strong> 丁冬亮、闫加辉、张立标、张君霞</p>
